OL,3,CRoyal Mail set to cut deliveries as
OL,4,Cpart of cost-saving proposals
OL,6,FThe Post Office - which is separate
OL,7,Ffrom Royal Mail - has objected to the
OL,8,Fplans, ITV New's Will Tullis reports
OL,10,FRoyal Mail should be allowed to cut
OL,11,FSaturday deliveries for second class
OL,12,Fletters in order save millions of
OL,13,Fpounds a year and protect the future
OL,14,Fof the UK's postal service, the
OL,15,Fregulator has proposed.
OL,17,FPlans put forward by Ofcom, if
OL,18,Fimplemented, would also reduce second
OL,19,Fclass letter deliveries to every other
OL,20,Fweekday.
