OL,3,CRoyal Mail set to cut deliveries as
OL,4,Cpart of cost-saving proposals
OL,6,FThe regulator said that after a
OL,7,Fconsultation, it had concluded
OL,8,Freducing the second class letter
OL,9,Fservice while maintaining first class
OL,10,Fdeliveries six days a week, would
OL,11,Fcontinue to meet postal users' needs
OL,12,Fand would save Royal Mail between #250
OL,13,Fmillion and #425 million a year.
OL,15,FThe outlined plans also include cuts
OL,16,Fto Royal Mail's main delivery targets
OL,17,F- for first class mail from 93% to 90%
OL,18,Fdelivered the next day, and for second
OL,19,Fclass mail from 98.5% to 95% delivered
OL,20,Fwithin three days.
