OL,3,CRoyal Mail set to cut deliveries as
OL,4,Cpart of cost-saving proposals
OL,6,FIt also comes after hefty fines
OL,7,Fagainst the company for poor
OL,8,Fperformance, with the group hit with
OL,9,Fmore than #16 million in penalties in
OL,10,Fthe past 18 months for failing to meet
OL,11,Ftargets.
OL,13,FLast year, Royal Mail's owner
OL,14,FInternational Distributions Services
OL,15,Fcalled for second class letter
OL,16,Fdeliveries to be axed from six days a
OL,17,Fweek to "every other weekday".
OL,19,FRishi Sunak's Conservative Government
OL,20,Fwas against the move.
