OL,3,CRoyal Mail set to cut deliveries as
OL,4,Cpart of cost-saving proposals
OL,6,FThe changes to the Universal Service
OL,7,FObligation (USO) come as Royal Mail is
OL,8,Fbeing sold to Czech billionaire Daniel
OL,9,FKretinsky for #3.6 billion, with the
OL,10,Fdeal cleared by the Government at the
OL,11,Fend of last year.
OL,13,FMr Kretinsky has pledged to stick to
OL,14,Fthe USO after the takeover.
OL,16,FThe Post Office - which is separate
OL,17,Ffrom Royal Mail - has objected to the
OL,18,Fplans.
