OL,3,CRoyal Mail set to cut deliveries as
OL,4,Cpart of cost-saving proposals
OL,6,F"Our postmasters and customers,
OL,7,Fparticularly those who are vulnerable,
OL,8,Fdo not want to see a reduction in the
OL,9,FUniversal Service Obligation", said a
OL,10,FPost Office spokesperson.
OL,12,F"The proposals announced today put
OL,13,Fmore pressure on postmasters who are
OL,14,Falready facing tough trading
OL,15,Fconditions".
OL,17,FThe Communication Workers Union (CWU)
OL,18,Falso warned the overhaul must come
OL,19,Fwith service improvements and better
OL,20,Fworking conditions for Royal Mail
OL,21,Fstaff.
